description:
Add new message types to claraity-vscode/src/types.ts and claraity-vscode/shared/protocol.ts (if it exists):

ClientMessage additions:
  | { type: 'list_subagents' }
  | { type: 'save_subagent'; name: string; description: string; system_prompt: string; tools?: string[]; is_fork?: boolean }
  | { type: 'delete_subagent'; name: string }
  | { type: 'reload_subagents' }

ServerMessage additions (in shared/protocol.ts):
  | { type: 'subagents_list'; subagents: SubAgentInfo[] }
  | { type: 'subagent_saved'; success: boolean; name: string; message: string }
  | { type: 'subagent_deleted'; success: boolean; name: string; message: string }

WebViewMessage additions:
  | { type: 'listSubagents' }
  | { type: 'saveSubagent'; name: string; description: string; systemPrompt: string; tools?: string[]; isFork?: boolean }
  | { type: 'deleteSubagent'; name: string }
  | { type: 'forkSubagent'; name: string }
  | { type: 'openSubagentFile'; name: string }

New interface: SubAgentInfo { name, description, system_prompt, tools, source: 'builtin'|'project'|'user', config_path? }

Files: claraity-vscode/src/types.ts, claraity-vscode/shared/protocol.ts (check if exists)
